          "reviewBody": "I am very much satisfied with the school and the staff. Teachers are holding their responsibility very firmly and my child is very happy and friendly with all his subject teachers and his class teacher Dimple ma'am. Parents are always welcomed with open hearts be on phone Or on physical visit to school. Thanks TVS and all teachers for developing my child morally mentally physically .",
