            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "TVS is a very good school focusing on overall development of the students. The primary focus on academics is not ignored while involving students in multiple extra curricular activities. This was the prime criteria I was looking for in a school for my child. Teachers are good and fully aware  and interested of students' overall milestones and performance. The principal also makes lot of efforts to stay updated with every class. Best part is the feedback system on students and from parents. The school is willing to go an extra mile.\nThis school has it all to groom talented holistic individuals who can succeed in fields of their choice.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
